Package: MarkovChain
Type: Package
Title: Implements basic Markov Chain on CPU and on GPU with OpenACC
Version: 1.0
Date: 2016-09-06
Author: Dmitry Mikushin
Maintainer: Dmitry Mikushin <dmitry@parallel-computing.pro>
Description: Given the stream of characters, computes the alphabet and the transition matrix for Markov Chain generation. Using the computed transition matrix, generates Markov Chains of characters.
License: LGPL v3
LazyData: TRUE
Imports: Rcpp (>= 0.11.0)
LinkingTo: Rcpp
